title: Wanderlust
description: Katie and Travis discuss where they would like to live for one year. Travis has a review of Click Bait (Spoiler Alert 13:56-18:35). What happened at the VMA’s (18:36) and AMC needs to get realistic (24:36). Tom Brady…still good (35:40). Urban Meyer’s NFL tenure is off to a bad start (40:34). Daniel Snyder…fix your stadium (51:41). Jameis Winston was prepared (1:15:50). Joe Judge is no longer a football guy (1:21:25). Can you propose after a loss (1:42:20) and can you take engagement photos while wearing jerseys (2:00:00)?

itunes:subtitle: Katie and Travis discuss the NFL, cats, shoeys and more
